User(user_id PK, name, email UNIQUE, password_hash, created_at)

Movie(movie_id PK, title, language, genre, duration)

Theater(theater_id PK, name, city)

Show(show_id PK, movie_id FK, theater_id FK, show_time, screen_no)

Seat(seat_id PK, show_id FK, seat_number, status)

Booking(booking_id PK, user_id FK, show_id FK, seat_id FK, status, booking_time)


| Method | Endpoint                           | Description              |
| ------ | ---------------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| POST   | `/users/register`                  | Create a user            |
| POST   | `/users/login`                     | Login/authenticate user  |
| GET    | `/movies?city=XYZ`                 | List movies in city      |
| GET    | `/shows?movieId=123&theaterId=456` | Showtimes for a movie    |
| GET    | `/shows/{id}/seats`                | Available seats for show |
| POST   | `/bookings`                        | Book selected seats      |



User → App → POST /bookings
          → Booking Service
              → Fetch seat with FOR UPDATE
              → Mark seat as BOOKED
              → Save Booking
              → (Mock) Payment
              → Return Confirmation

